title: NFL ATL: Who will be the 2014 Team of ATL?
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Who will be the 2014 Team of ATL?
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- whittles down its candidates for 2014’s "Team of Around the League," introducing the franchises who seem to have the most intrigue and heaviest fun factor surrounding them this preseason.  Elsewhere, as always, the gang discusses the latest headlines from across the NFL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
